**Town Elder** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous | Haunted
__Basics__
The Town Elder will survive the first night attack against them, but death will be due to old age, causing them to become banished witout becoming a ghost first.
__Details__
The Town Elder will not be notified of their defence being used.
If the Town Elder dies *before* using their defence (i.e. lynching or day kill), then they will become a ghost as normal.

__Simplified__
The Town Elder will survive the first night attack against them, but death will be due to old age, causing them to become banished witout becoming a ghost first.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `Attacks` through Passive Defense during Night (~UntilUse)

__Card__
The Town Elder can survive one attack before dying of old age.
